<tr>
<th>Stage</th>
<th>Agent</th>
<th>Output</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>1</td>
<td>Mission / Profile Analyst</td>
<td>Reads the pitch or profile, frames the world it improves, casts your founder seat</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>2</td>
<td>Org Designer</td>
<td>Designs a digital-workforce blueprint <em>for this specific venture</em></td>
